Turkey’s Esas Will Invest $100 Million in Hospitals, Aksam Says

-- B y   B e n j a m i n   H a r v e y
-- 
2011-10-12T06:27:02Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-12/turkey-s-esas-will-invest-100-million-in-hospitals-aksam-says.html
Turkey ’s Esas Holding AS plans to
invest $100 million in its hospital chain during the next three
years,  Aksam  reported, citing Esas chairman Erhan Kamisli.  The holding has consolidated its health-care investments in
a company called Medline Saglik Grubu, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
